"ai": "catalog:"
```

The `ai` and `@ai-sdk/gateway` packages are already used by `apps/app` and `packages/app-rerank`. Verify the exact catalog version and match.

### Success Criteria

#### Automated Verification

- [ ] `pnpm install` succeeds after adding the workspace dep.
- [ ] `pnpm --filter @api/platform typecheck` passes.
- [ ] `pnpm --filter @api/platform build` succeeds.
- [ ] `pnpm typecheck` passes at the root.
- [ ] `pnpm check` passes.

#### Manual Verification

