1	/**
2	 * Proxy tRPC sub-router.
3	 *
4	 * Ported from apps/gateway/src/routes/connections.ts (proxy endpoints).
5	 * All procedures use serviceProcedure (JWT auth required).
6	 *
7	 * listEndpoints: Returns the provider's API catalog (strips Zod responseSchema).
8	 * execute: Pure authenticated API proxy with 401-retry pattern.
